    ---
    
    ### **NovaLens Pricing Tiers Comparison**
    
    | **Feature**               | **Professional**                          | **Business**                              |
    |---------------------------|-------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------------|
    | **Target Audience**       | Individual professionals, small teams    | Mid-sized to large enterprises            |
    | **Monthly Cost**          | **$4,000/month**                          | **$12,000/month**                         |
