    | **Priority Support**      | ❌ (Standard support)                     | ✅ (Dedicated account manager + 24/7 SLA) |
    | **SLA (Response Time)**   | 24-hour response                          | 1-hour response for critical issues       |
    | **Team Collaboration**    | Basic (shared folders)                    | Advanced (role-based access, audit logs)  |
    | **Integration Options**   | REST API, Zapier, Webhooks                | REST API, Zapier, Webhooks, **SDKs (Python, Java)**, Salesforce/HubSpot plugins |
    | **Compliance**            | SOC 2 Type II                             | SOC 2 Type II, HIPAA, GDPR                |
    | **Training & Onboarding** | Self-service                              | Custom onboarding + training sessions     |
    | **Free Trial**            | 14 days                                   | 14 days (with enterprise demo)            |
    
