    9. **Amazon S3**
    10. **Google Cloud Storage (GCS)**
    11. **Azure Blob Storage**
    12. **Parquet/CSV/JSON (direct upload)**
    
    ### **Business Applications & APIs**
    13. **Salesforce**
    14. **HubSpot**
    15. **Google Analytics 4 (GA4)**
    16. **Stripe**
    17. **Shopify**
    18. **REST APIs (custom connectors)**
    
    ### **Real-Time & Streaming Sources**
    19. **Kafka**
    20. **Amazon Kinesis**
    
    ### **Other Integrations**
    21. **dbt (for transformed data models)**
    22. **Fivetran (via supported destinations)**
    23. **Airbyte (via supported destinations)**
    
    For the most up-to-date list, check the **NovaLens documentation** ([docs.novalens.ai](https://docs.novalens.ai)) or the **"Add Data Source"** section in the product UI.
    
