    This policy applies to all eligible employees as outlined in the **NovaAI On-Call Policy (v3.2, last updated March 15, 2024)**. Employees in roles requiring on-call duties (e.g., Site Reliability Engineers, DevOps, and certain Support roles) are covered under this policy.
    
